Definition: a radical terrorist group that broke away in 1997 when the mainstream Provisional IRA proposed a cease-fire
Example: has continued terrorist activities in opposition to any peace agreement
Synonyms: Real_Irish_Republican_Army, RIRA, Dissident_Irish_Republican_Army, terrorist_organization, i, noun, act, terrorism, c, location, Ireland, r, a, radical, terrorist, group, that, broke, away, in, when, the, mainstream, Provisional, IRA, proposed, cease-fire, has, continued, activities, opposition, to, any, peace, agreement
Category: noun.group
